Question: Many universities require that freshman live on campus dorm during the first year of college. In your opinion, is this a good or a bad thing? Explain your opinion on this issue.
Answer:
I like the idea that freshman live on campus during the first year of college. It gives them a lot opportunities to get familiar with the college life, to make friends, to join the social societies. A lot students don't have cars so it will be very convenient for them live on campus.